You can also leave your autograph on the walls in Bodeguita, Havana.
The bar of the expensive Hotel Nacional will mix a cocktail according to your wishes.
And those iconic cars from the 50s are still driving around Havana, because the once imported Žigulíks and Fiats have long rotted in that salty and humid air.
