About coffee, rum, cigars, about the Sierra Maestra, about the Bay of Pigs and the Isla de Pinos, about the cabaret Tropicana, about the shrine of the Cuban patroness Caridad del Cobre, about santeria, about African religions professed by the descendants of former slaves, all this could be described many pages.
