Former Defense Minister José Bono accepted an offer from Prime Minister and Socialist Secretary General José Luis Rodríguez Zapatero to head the PSOE (Spanish Workers' Socialist Party) list in Toledo in the next general election and become President of Congress if the Socialists win the general election.
